name: Blue Bag
description:
T & T purses and clutches are made by a talented Argentinian designer. Her passion to create fine leather accessories made T & T brand born. All leather purses capture the basics of leather making, they are elaborated by hand and made with the finest materials. The products are lined and coated with a leather protectant. All T & T products are sold with a fabric bag to keep it save from any damage.

Description: 
Blue genuine leather cross body with rivets on cover and an adjustable strap. 
All Purses are made to order and will be made specially for you, 100% handmade. Please allow up to four weeks for your order to be completed. 
Material: Suede 
Size: 8.5in x 8.5in x 2.5in 
Shipping: priority mail with tracking number
